        void acceptMembersOfGroup(ExternalUserGroup group,
                          ExternalEntityVisitor<Long> visitor)
                   throws ExternalUserGroupAccessorException
        This method can be used to visit all members of the given group. The visitor visits only users which are already a member within Communote, though it only works on their id.
        Parameters:
        group - The child group.
        visitor - A visitor for visiting the found entities.
